# AI-Powered Research Paper Summarizer

## Features
- RAG-based Question Answering
- Gemini AI Integration
- Knowledge Graph (Neo4j)
- Streamlit UI

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- LangChain
- FAISS
- Neo4j
- Gemini API

## Run
streamlit run main.py